{"title":"人生","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1983,"month":3,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"人生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞬息云烟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为时多么短暂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被时光带走的一切哟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远不再回还。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生命有如文火徐燃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"死亡将是永恒久远，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因需求而产生的一切哟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正是我们的意愿。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼前的万物，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即将消失，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"理想和激情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也会化作虚无的云烟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对你从事的事业，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"魔鬼可能在一旁讪笑；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千百万人拚命争夺，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也许是无谓的辛劳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心乱气恼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是世上一切祸患的根苗；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊慌烦忧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"意谓“幸福已经遁逃”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无聊的目标，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也可能被人苦苦追求；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"转眼即逝的人生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正是一次激情的战斗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心胸狭窄的人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往往自命伟大不凡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这种人的命运啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有自怨自惭。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}